00:08:57.162 --> 00:08:58.246 align:middle line:90%
or a new reality?

00:08:58.246 --> 00:09:00.415 align:middle line:84%
>> SEAMAN: Yeah, well, let's
look at what's actually

00:09:00.415 --> 00:09:01.207 align:middle line:90%
happened.

00:09:01.207 --> 00:09:03.126 align:middle line:84%
"The Washington Post"
is a great example.

00:09:03.126 --> 00:09:06.212 align:middle line:84%
