And you go back further,
Woodward and Bernstein-- that's

00:09:16.431 --> 00:09:18.516 align:middle line:84%
the reason why people trust
"The Washington Post,"

00:09:18.516 --> 00:09:22.312 align:middle line:84%
is that that was the banner
