00:09:27.650 --> 00:09:30.570 align:middle line:84%
And I think this has happened
in different areas of society,

00:09:30.570 --> 00:09:31.988 align:middle line:90%
not just the media.

00:09:31.988 --> 00:09:33.698 align:middle line:90%
You look at the US dollar.

00:09:33.698 --> 00:09:37.827 align:middle line:84%
From Nixon onward, it's just
been a promise, just a note

00:09:37.827 --> 00:09:40.413 align:middle line:84%
