tell, it would actually work.

00:13:36.816 --> 00:13:38.609 align:middle line:84%
It's First-Amendment
protected activity.

00:13:38.609 --> 00:13:41.279 align:middle line:84%
And I know there have been
attempts in states like Indiana

00:13:41.279 --> 00:13:44.407 align:middle line:84%
