00:14:26.199 --> 00:14:27.867 align:middle line:84%
whenever you break
out of that, you're

00:14:27.867 --> 00:14:29.827 align:middle line:84%
doing something
that is spiritual.

00:14:29.827 --> 00:14:32.455 align:middle line:84%
And you look at the US,
the founding fathers,

00:14:32.455 --> 00:14:34.790 align:middle line:84%
