we're into cannabis.

00:14:34.790 --> 00:14:36.084 align:middle line:90%
We don't know that for sure.

00:14:36.084 --> 00:14:37.627 align:middle line:84%
What we do know for
sure is that they

00:14:37.627 --> 00:14:39.420 align:middle line:90%
were into the hemp industry.

00:14:39.420 --> 00:14:42.340 align:middle line:84%
And then we know other Western
thinkers like Shakespeare, they

00:14:42.340 --> 00:14:44.050 align:middle line:90%
believe, were using cannabis.

00:14:44.050 --> 00:14:48.221 align:middle line:84%
They found THC residue in
one of his smoking pipes.

00:14:48.221 --> 00:14:50.389 align:middle line:84%
Why didn't make a big
deal out of it then?

00:14:50.389 --> 00:14:52.433 align:middle line:84%
It was not regulated
or criminalized.

00:14:52.433 --> 00:14:56.813 align:middle line:84%
So your average adult man who
was in an intellectual field

00:14:56.813 --> 00:14:59.065 align:middle line:84%
might have just used
cannabis, and there

00:14:59.065 --> 00:15:00.817 align:middle line:84%
would have been no
public discussion of it

00:15:00.817 --> 00:15:02.485 align:middle line:84%
because it would be
like drinking a tea.

00:15:02.485 --> 00:15:03.861 align:middle line:90%
Why would you point that out?

00:15:03.861 --> 00:15:05.029 align:middle line:90%
>> SEAMAN: Well, absolutely.

00:15:05.029 --> 00:15:06.614 align:middle line:84%
I mean, frankly we
know historically

00:15:06.614 --> 00:15:10.326 align:middle line:84%
that drugs were often used
for initiatory purposes

00:15:10.326 --> 00:15:11.494 align:middle line:90%
within religious contexts.

00:15:11.494 --> 00:15:13.162 align:middle line:84%
And frankly, the
biggest argument

00:15:13.162 --> 00:15:15.581 align:middle line:84%
