big-government regulated,

00:16:00.168 --> 00:16:02.670 align:middle line:84%
anti-cannabis states,
in my opinion.

00:16:02.670 --> 00:16:06.841 align:middle line:84%
And she has access to it now,
thanks to them moving forward.

00:16:06.841 --> 00:16:10.720 align:middle line:84%
Massachusetts has
legal recreational.

00:16:10.720 --> 00:16:11.637 align:middle line:90%
That's been enacted.

00:16:11.637 --> 00:16:13.181 align:middle line:90%
So just a matter of time now.

00:16:13.181 --> 00:16:15.600 align:middle line:84%
I never thought I'd
see within my lifetime

00:16:15.600 --> 00:16:18.394 align:middle line:84%
