weed in Boston.

00:16:18.394 --> 00:16:20.104 align:middle line:90%
I guess it makes sense, right?

00:16:20.104 --> 00:16:23.107 align:middle line:84%
The original Tea
Party started there.

00:16:23.107 --> 00:16:24.567 align:middle line:90%
So that's interesting.

